posts.post_title: FS: T206's with paper loss on back
posts.post_content:
I will be updating this thread periodically as I have a lot to list. I will sort them into teams when I scan them so it is easier.

These all have paper loss on the backs. Some of the fronts are quite good. Check the scans for a detailed idea. 




Looking to sell as singles, mini lots, one big lot, doesn't matter to me. If you have an offer, PM me and will respond quickly.



I have most teams so if you have a request, just ask or send a PM. Wanted to just get a few up to start.
